{"tid":272481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地班地鐵狗係咪唔識行入啲？","createTime":"2017-06-06T00:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T03:08:29.000Z","uid":10845,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"066b35a66d2cfe9703b4e0e003526246e30f1c9f","tid":272481,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:46:28.000Z","msg":"我真係屌撚爆你班自尻私既懶惰閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n永遠入撚左車都擺副冇位好迫既樣出黎<br />\n明明入面咁撚多位。係要企門口位為乜姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫你行入啲好似殺左你老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人其實都唔係高質得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9b8969f4ff6ffca4e191a72369ec61503af862","tid":272481,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:48:21.000Z","msg":"咁迫點玩電話"},{"pid":"aadf013123021bf38f5024d8cb638d9c06cc2d2d","tid":272481,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:48:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁迫點玩電話</blockquote><br />\n行入去咪大把位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d4f410947a0aed256420d0dbf7c1fb6dccdd16","tid":272481,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:50:54.000Z","msg":"近門口中間根本唔應該種柱"},{"pid":"d706857deacec137f5a70cb69656edc2d87dd1cd","tid":272481,"uid":104658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:52:29.000Z","msg":"下個站落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行咗入去下個站又要迫返出黎，係咁要講唔該借借，除時落唔到車"},{"pid":"2db9a8fccf42658a17a5063caf6d5f53c745451a","tid":272481,"uid":22989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:53:29.000Z","msg":"樓主做波板糖人？"},{"pid":"de0a09509eef5ba107510cedff4250a5a2aa3ca4","tid":272481,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:55:10.000Z","msg":"豬車係咁"},{"pid":"435a2c715c2131bb