s/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c50c1fbfdfcf3ffe9e4117ad5d95ae384d0114","tid":272481,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T03:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主做波板糖人？</blockquote><br />\n岩岩上唔到車啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}